https://adventofcode.com/2022

Build and run all programs:

	$ ./build

File naming convention:

	01.in0          # Example input values of day 1
	01.in1          # Final input values of day 1
	01.in2          # Extra test input if needed
	01a.c           # Source code of day 1 part 1
	01a             # Compiled program of day 1 part 1
	01b.c           # Source code of day 1 part 2
	01b             # Compiled program of day 1 part 2

	02.in0          # Example input values of day 2
	02a.c           # Source code of day 2 part 1
	                # ...
